            <p>Bishop J. W. Colenso supports his old contention that the Kaffirs (including Zulus of South Africa) are Negroes.</p> 
<p>[Horace Waller’s] <hi rend="italic">The last journals of David Livingstone</hi> [<hi rend="italic">in central Africa</hi> (1874)] cites CD’s plant research and has many facts "for Darwin".</p> 
